{
  "texts": [
    "Since most of this research focuses on canonical computer science applications, it is only indirectly relevant for economics.",
    "The incentives for leakage of economically relevant text pieces into the training datasets of LLMs is potentially different.",
    "How much should we worry that naive uses of LLMs in economic prediction problems suffer from training leakage?",
    "To answer this question, we next test for training leakage in two empirical settings relevant to economists.",
    "We first assess training leakage in an empirical setting relevant for economists studying politics and political economy: congressional legislation."
  ]
}